details.details: Held by Labor since 2004 with current margin of 10.4%.

Aston was won by the Liberal Party's Alan Tudge with a margin of 2.8% at the last Federal election. It has been a safe Liberal seat for three decade. It was gained by Labor at an April 2023 by-election, the first time in a century that a government had gained a seat from the opposition at a Federal by-election.
